sudo apt-get install redis-server
pip install redis
pip install django-redis-cache

------------------------------------
Go to this path /etc/redis/redis.conf
------------------------------------

Comment the code:
----------------
port 6379
bind 127.0.0.1

Uncomment the code:
------------------
unixsocket /var/run/redis/redis.sock
unixsocketperm 700
restart server:
sudo service redis-server restart



